name: Rainbow
description:
Origami Cranes symbolize peace, long life, good luck and prosperity

This exquisite handmade rainbow of colours mobile would be a happy addition to any nursery as it will suit any decor.

The cascading cranes are jewelled to perfection hanging on beading wire.

It is the perfect gift for a boy or a girl.

It's dimenions are 23 cm wide and approx 65cm long.

Packaged in a box for postage the cranes are folded flat for preservation.

name: 4 Season
description:
The perfect non gender specific gift.  This exquisit mobile has Japanese origami paper themed with the four seasons. Spring, Winter, Summer and Autumn.

Enhanced with precious beading to bring it to it's full potention.  This is a very popular mobile with only one left.

It's dimenions are 23 cm wide and approx 65cm long.

name: Dream Catcher
description:
Dream Catcher is the perfect addition to any room.  This quirky design is very eye catching.

It is consists of 2 hand folded Origami cranes evenly hung in a decorated hanging circle. 

It hangs 32 cm long and is 23 cm wide.

Boxed and packaged for postage.  The cranes are folded flat to preserve them.
